{"tid":1001828,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普捷天奴唔保證下季執掌熱刺","createTime":"2019-01-30T12:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T13:20:03.000Z","uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"78f20a70c165245097b17616c8ebe9b4956c479a","tid":1001828,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=69f03862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】儘管熱刺領隊普捷天奴打算完成與球隊之間的合約，但他不能保證下季仍然會在熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n「我不能保證這一點，這取決於班主的心情，球會的決定，這不僅僅是我的決定。」普捷天奴（Mauricio Pochettino）說，「我簽了5年，我尊重我的合約。但簽下一份5年合約並不代表你永遠都會在這裡。」<br />\n<br />\n最近有報道指普捷天奴與曼聯及皇家馬德里等大球會有聯繫，他更被視為是下任曼聯領隊的頭號人選。46歲的普捷天奴於去年5月與熱刺簽下5年半合約，雖然他打算履行合約直至完結，但就無法保證下季仍會留在熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n他補充，「我熱愛自己的工作，當然我喜歡挑戰。當我到達熱刺時，我非常清楚這挑戰會很艱難。我是一個非常積極的人，我將緊貼這支球隊直到最後，以幫助球會實現他們想要的一切。」<br />\n<br />\n熱刺VS屈福特<br />\nNow622台31/01 04:00直播"},{"pid":"71c8a63c399b6d8fbd120e6d26789d86e3f684f2","tid":1001828,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">LET GO HAWKS</span></span>"},{"pid":"7506ca499cafd3b10f3af396ac8662f5edfb0611","tid":1001828,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"Daddy d 9up係咪會人傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cc138d94ee1d637d42691bd2c52dbb0fc58a00","tid":1001828,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c8a63c399b6d8fbd120e6d26789d86e3f684f2","tid":1001828,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">LET GO HAWKS</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"鷹隊打MMA會點